---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Web API Development">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-plug"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Robust APIs that Power Modern Applications</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies builds secure, scalable Web APIs and RESTful services that connect your web and mobile applications, enable third-party integrations and provide a clean data layer your business can build on — documented, tested and ready to deploy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-exchange"></i></div>
            <h5>RESTful API Design</h5>
            <p>Design and development of clean RESTful web services with JSON and XML responses, following REST best practices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-lock"></i></div>
            <h5>Authentication &amp; Security</h5>
            <p>OAuth 2.0, JWT and API key authentication with SSL/TLS encryption, rate limiting and input validation built in from the start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></div>
            <h5>Third-party Integration</h5>
            <p>Seamless integration with payment gateways, social media platforms, CRM systems and other third-party services.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-file-text-o"></i></div>
            <h5>API Documentation</h5>
            <p>Comprehensive API documentation using Swagger and OpenAPI specifications so developers can integrate quickly and confidently.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-shield"></i></div>
            <h5>Secure Data Handling</h5>
            <p>Encrypted data transfer, secure offsite backup and disaster recovery planning ensure your critical data is always protected.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-tachometer"></i></div>
            <h5>Performance &amp; Scalability</h5>
            <p>High-performance API architecture with caching strategies and horizontal scaling to handle growing request volumes smoothly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
